## 
## data:  y
## Chi-squared = 12.5, df = 20, p-value = 0.8978
Box.test(y^2,20,type='Ljung')
## 
##  Box-Ljung test
## 
## data:  y^2
## X-squared = 36.015, df = 20, p-value = 0.01532
tdx=c(1:252)+12
